collectible.name: First Anon's Human Face - Venice
collectible.description: Even without expression, meditating on infinity, we could see the discreet smile of interest and curiosity that appeared on Anon's face, its desire to help  Christie to find Love. That was the first moment that Anon had a face, and it was a Venetian, Carnival face mask! They say that if you go to Venice and meet Christie, you will feel the same sensation that Anon felt: the beginning of an experience, the beginning of a search.
